title: Roni Benise - 6 Albums Flamenco & Spanish Guitar
description:
Hello guys, I previously uploaded this torrent and then deleted it because of some mistakes I found. Now I'm re-uploading. As I've stated before I found these in a Russian forum so thanks goes to them. 

Do note that I found some songs (maybe 2 or 3?)that have different names but are the same. 

Included albums are:

Carnaval/Brazil (2003)
Mediterranea (2002)
Nights Of Fire!
Nights Of Fire! (Extras) (2005)
Romance & Passion/Europa (2001)
Spanish Nights (2001)
Taboo (2000)

Enjoy.
